{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Living Savior Preschool -}{\plain \fs24 \f8  The children sang beautifully at their Spring Program on Wednesday. This year's theme \softline
was "We're Going To The Zoo" and the children even sang about God's floating zoo - Noah's Ark! An art show was \softline
also part of the program and the children were excited to show off their art skills and creativity. On Friday we \softline
welcomed Max, a therapy dog and his handler as he read a story about Max's adventures. \par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
